Would be nice.
Where .Data.FormBodyType is read from 
GET variables. Unfortunately because templates
call each other, and this uses vm,
it would require .Data variables from the top 
to be transmitted to the next template and so on.
And it may not be great for security.

OTOH, these files are static.
